    html: "<p>I don’t normally talk about Airsoft unless it related to competitive shooting or providing an avenue for cross over to sports shooting. This however is a special case as it provides more realism to what I had always seen as an issue with Automatic Electric Guns, the unrealistic trigger pull. This new product aims to resolve this!</p>\n\n<figure><div>\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"PERUN CLICKER | The Most Realistic Trigger Feel On v2 AEGs ? *AIRSOFT REPLICA*\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/idpxfIJSkvA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n<p>The Perun Clicker Trigger is a high-quality trigger that is designed specifically for the V2 gearbox of an airsoft AEG. This trigger is made of durable and lightweight aluminium, and features a unique “clicker” mechanism that provides a distinct and satisfying trigger pull. In this article, we will review the Perun Clicker Trigger and discuss its features, benefits, and how to install it on your airsoft gun.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"features\">Features</h2>\n\n<p>The Perun Clicker Trigger is made of high-quality aluminium, which makes it both durable and lightweight. The trigger features a unique “clicker” mechanism that provides a distinct and satisfying trigger pull. This mechanism is adjustable, allowing you to fine-tune the trigger pull to your liking. Additionally, the trigger features a pre-travel adjustment screw, which can help you reduce the amount of travel required before the trigger breaks.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"benefits\">Benefits</h2>\n\n<p>One of the primary benefits of the Perun Clicker Trigger is its unique “clicker” mechanism. This mechanism provides a distinct and satisfying trigger pull, which can help improve your accuracy and overall shooting experience. Additionally, the adjustable pre-travel and clicker mechanisms allow you to fine-tune the trigger pull to your liking, giving you greater control and precision when firing your airsoft gun.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"installation\">Installation</h2>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>NOTE: This trigger requires the use of a Perun Hybrid board to work with your gearbox!</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Installing the Perun Clicker Trigger is relatively straightforward, but it does require some basic knowledge of airsoft gun mechanics. Before installing the trigger, you should ensure that your airsoft gun’s gearbox is properly lubricated and in good working order. You will also need to disassemble the gearbox and remove the existing trigger.</p>\n\n<p>Once the old trigger has been removed, you can install the Perun Clicker Trigger in its place. The trigger comes with a set of instructions that provide detailed information on how to install it, but the process generally involves attaching the trigger to the gearbox using screws or pins.</p>\n\n<p>Once the trigger is installed, you will need to test it to ensure that it is functioning properly. This can be done by dry firing the gun and checking for any issues with the trigger pull. If everything is working correctly, you can reassemble the gearbox and begin using your airsoft gun with the new trigger.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"conclusion\">Conclusion</h2>\n\n<p>Overall, the Perun Clicker Trigger is an excellent upgrade for anyone looking to improve the trigger pull on their airsoft AEG. Its unique “clicker” mechanism provides a distinct and satisfying trigger pull, and its adjustable pre-travel and clicker mechanisms allow you to fine-tune the trigger pull to your liking. Additionally, its durable and lightweight aluminium construction makes it a reliable and long-lasting upgrade for your airsoft gun. If you’re looking to improve your airsoft shooting experience, the Perun Clicker Trigger is definitely worth considering.</p>",
